snippet.title: Pikmin 3 Deluxe Hack: CHAOMIN
snippet.description:
It's Chaomin!

Download: https://gamebanana.com/mods/473137

2 new mission levels, new music, new game models, new treasure, and much more! I had a lot of fun making and playing this hack, and I hope you all enjoy it! 

I'd like to see what does better in this hack for either improvement to this hack or my next hack. Let me know if you want to see more levels in this hack or what you would like to see next. Your comments are appreciated! :)

If you enjoy my modding content, please be sure to like the video or subscribe to my channel. 

Thanks to everyone in the community for helping me out with this hack, I couldn't have done it without them.

Q: What are Chao? 
A: https://chao-island.com/info-center/about-chao

Pikmin 3 Hacking Discord: https://discord.gg/G7Pgkdh
Music for the Video: https://soundcloud.com/hyperpotions/chaodancemix
Donate: https://www.paypal.com/donate/?business=AVJWNKBZ86QZL&no_recurring=0&item_name=While+all+mods+and+content+are+completely+free%2C+any+support+you+provide+me+is+appreciated+and+keeps+me+motivated.+Thank+you+%3A%29&currency_code=USD
Discord: https://discord.gg/BzfGuMbM8K 

All other sources used in this mod are in the README for this hack. 

#pikmin3 #pikmin #romhack #switch #nintendoswitch #pikmin3deluxe #chaogarden #sonicchaos
